# 止蝕  
(pos:動詞)  
<explanation>  
yue:阻止損失或減少損失嘅行為（量詞：唔使）  
eng:to stop losses / to prevent further loss  
<eg>  
yue:公司今年營收減少，所以經理叫大家要止蝕。 (gung1 si1 gam1 nin4 jing4 sau1 zin2 hau5, so2 ging1 lei4 giu3 daa1 gaa1 jiu5 zi2 sik1.)  
eng:The company's revenue has decreased this year, so the manager asked everyone to stop losses.  

yue:股票跌咗好耐，無使急，應該止蝕先。 (gau2 piu6 dit3 zo2 hou2 noi6, mou4 sai2 gap1, jing1 gaa1 zi2 sik1 sin1.)  
eng:The stock has fallen for a long time, no need to panic, should stop losses first.  

yue:呢次賭博唔掂，應即刻止蝕。 (ni1 ci3 dou2 bok1 m4 dim6, jing1 gik1 zi2 sik1.)  
eng:This time gambling didn't work out, should stop losses immediately.  

yue:止蝕唔使急，睇埋個勢再行動。 (zi2 sik1 mou4 sai2 gap1, tai2 maai4 go3 si6 zoi6 hang4 dung6.)  
eng:Don't rush to stop losses, assess the situation before acting.  

yue:呢間小店經常止蝕，難以長期經營。 (ni1 gin3 siu2 dim3 ging1 soeng4 zi2 sik1, naan4 ji5 coeng4 kei4.)  
eng:This small shop often stops losses, making long-term operation difficult.  

yue:止蝕先至可以扭轉局面。 (zi2 sik1 sin1 zi2 jiu5 jyun2 zyun3 zyun6 ji6.)  
eng:Only by stopping losses can the situation be reversed.  

yue:呢場戲已經開始差，應及早止蝕。 (ni1 coeng4 hei3 ji5 hoi2 si2 ca1, jing1 gik1 zi2 sik1.)  
eng:The play has already started poorly, should stop losses early.  

yue:止蝕唔好拖，愈拖愈大。 (zi2 sik1 mou4 hou2 to1, jyu5 to1 jyu5 daai6.)  
eng:Don't delay in stopping losses, the longer you delay, the bigger the loss.  

yue:呢次失敗係止蝕嘅契機。 (ni1 ci3 sik1 baai6 hai6 zi2 sik1 kaak1 kei1.)  
eng:This failure is an opportunity to stop losses.  

yue:止蝕之後再考慮反彈。 (zi2 sik1 zi1 hau6 zoi2 haau2 jyun4 taan4.)  
eng:Stop losses first, then consider a rebound.  

---

**解釋說明：**  
「止蝕」係廣東話中常用嘅金融與商業術語，原文「止蝕」即「阻止損失」，指當投資、經營或博鬥出現虧損時，採取措施停止繼續虧損嘅行為。呢詞多應用於股票、賭博、生意、戲劇或虧損局面前，強調及時收手以防損失擴大。  
粵語中「蝕」係「損失」之意（如「蚀本」、「蝕錢」），「止」即「阻止」。語法上可單用，亦可結合「先」、「先至」、「之後」等詞表示動作先後。  
日常用法中，亦可引申為「收手」、「不再繼續輸」，帶有策略性或被動性。  

**注意：**  
- 「止蝕」唔係「止血」，但有時會用嚟形容「停止虧損」，與「止血」有類似比喻用法。  
- 粵語中「止蝕」多作「停止虧損」解，唔係「阻止蝕蝕」（因「蝕」本身已含損失意義）。  
- 量詞「唔使」表示「毋須」或「不需」，反映止蝕係一種主動行動。  

此詞條收錄完畢，符合粵語語法與實用場景。 [end of text]


